<item>
            <title>[LU-17606] delete old kernel patch series</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17606</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are old ldiskfs patch series for el7.6-el7.8 that could be deleted from master without any concern of these old distro kernels being used for 2.16 servers.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is also likely that el8.0-el8.4 and Ubuntu19 could also be removed with little concern for these older releases being used anywhere, but that should be done in a separate patch&lt;/p&gt;</description>
